title: More time
comment: the time would be better used and we would lead a more orderly life

title: implant rejection
comment: it is necessary to take into account the cases where the human body rejects the implant and to know how to act in such cases

title: more productivity
comment: Productivity would increase significantly by being able to control the days of sleep

title: contribution to science
comment: The contribution to science of such an implant would be a great benefit, scientists could study sleep behavior more deeply, detect problems in advance and correct them

title: hacker attack
comment: A big problem would be if a hacker manages to take control of the implant. The consequences could be very serious depending on the intentions of the attacker

title: medical benefit
comment: The benefit of an implant capable of regulating sleep is immense. For example, many people who suffer from insomnia could be cured, also people with mental disorders caused by lack of sleep.
